bill_title: revise certain provisions regarding the closure of county and township roads due to high water.

bill_versions.bill_text: FOR AN ACT ENTITLED, An Act to revise certain provisions regarding the closure of county and township roads due to high water. BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF SOUTH DAKOTA: Section 1. The procedures to close certain county and township roads due to high water are hereby revised. 170 copies were printed on recycled paper by the South Dakota Legislative Research Council at a cost of $.098 per page. . Insertions into existing statutes are indicated by underscores. Deletions from existing statutes are indicated by overstrikes.
